      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "系数柱状图里，每根柱子的高度就是对应那一项的值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "generating-functions",
      "section_id": "conv",
      "line_id": "conv-1",
      "filename": "conv-conv-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/generating-functions/xiaoxiao/conv-conv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "两个生成函数相乘时，x 的 k 次项系数怎么来？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "generating-functions",
      "section_id": "conv",
      "line_id": "conv-2",
