      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "它把所有下标相加等于 k 的系数两两相乘再求和，这叫卷积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "generating-functions",
      "section_id": "conv",
      "line_id": "conv-3",
